title: Jessimae Peluso
itunes:title: Jessimae Peluso
description:
Stand-up comic Jessimae Peluso is on the pod and the bras come off in the first 15 minutes.  Between sips of tequila, Whitney and Jessimae laugh about vibrators, dead parents, and the foxiness of Jeff Goldblum.  Find Jessimae on her podcast Sharp Tongue, Tattoo Redo on Netflix, and on her newest podcast GYRL with Carly Aquilino exclusively on Patreon.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
